    "The proposed development does not comply with criteria 9A of Class MA, which states that \"Schedule 2 does not grant permission for, or authorise any development of, any new dwellinghouse that does not comply with the nationally described space standard issued by the Department for Communities and Local Government on 27th March 2015(1)\".",
